Q:在创建/修改方法的时候如何将当前操作的类作为方法的参数类型？
A:
  1.通过ClassCreator/EnumCreator/InterfaceCreator/ClassModifier的getCurrentClass方法获取当前操作的类比如
  creator.createStaticMethod("main", new AClass[]{creator.getCurrentClass()}, new String[]{"arg"}, null, null, Opcodes.ACC_PUBLIC, new StaticMethodBody(){...});
  
  2._当然还可以通过ProgramBlock的getMethodOwner方法获取比如
  creator.createStaticMethod("main", new AClass[]{AClassFactory.getProductClass(String[].class)}, new String[]{"args"}, null, null,
                Opcodes.ACC_PUBLIC + Opcodes.ACC_STATIC, new StaticMethodBody(){
        @Override
        public void generateBody(LocalVariable... argus) {
           invokeConstructor(getMethodOwner());
        }
  });